args ‚Üź ‚ÄĘargs
tab ‚Üź @+9
lf ‚Üź @+10
space ‚Üź @+32
empty ‚Üź ‚ü®‚ü©

Fail ‚Üź {ūĚēä code‚ÄŅmessage:
  ‚ÄĘOut "ERROR" ‚ąĺ tab ‚ąĺ code ‚ąĺ tab ‚ąĺ message
  ‚ÄĘExit 1
}

TrimLeft ‚Üź {ūĚēä xs: (+¬ī ‚ąß` (xs = space)) ‚Üď xs}
TrimRight ‚Üź {ūĚēä xs: ((‚Č† xs) - +¬ī ‚ąß` ((‚ĆĹ xs) = space)) ‚ÜĎ xs}
Trim ‚Üź {TrimRight TrimLeft ūĚē©}
UnsafeText ‚Üź {ūĚēä text:
  controls ‚Üź ((@+0) + ‚Üē32) ‚ąĺ ‚ü®@+127‚ü©
  ‚ą®¬ī 0 ‚ąĺ text ‚ąä controls
}
{ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"usage", "expected BASE TARGET DATE DESCRIPTION IDENTITY_MODE EVENT_ID POSTING_COUNT postings and optional metadata"‚ü©}‚ćü(9 > ‚Č† args) @
base ‚Üź 0 ‚äĎ args
target ‚Üź 1 ‚äĎ args
dateText ‚Üź 2 ‚äĎ args
description ‚Üź 3 ‚äĎ args
identityMode ‚Üź 4 ‚äĎ args
eventId ‚Üź 5 ‚äĎ args
postingCountText ‚Üź 6‚äĎargs
postingCount ‚Üź ‚ÄĘBQN postingCountText
{ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"posting_count_invalid", "posting count must be at least two"‚ü©}‚ćü((postingCount<2)‚ą®postingCount‚ČĘ‚ĆäpostingCount) @
{ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"posting_count_invalid", "posting count exceeds supplied arguments"‚ü©}‚ćü((7+postingCount)>‚Č†args) @
postingArgs ‚Üź postingCount‚ÜĎ7‚Üďargs
metadataArgs ‚Üź (7+postingCount)‚Üďargs

{ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"date_invalid", "date must be a valid YYYY-MM-DD calendar date"‚ü©}‚ćü(¬¨ dates.IsValidDateText dateText) @
{ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"description_invalid", "description must be nonempty and must not contain unsafe control input"‚ü©}‚ćü((0 = ‚Č† Trim description) ‚ą® (UnsafeText description) ‚ą® description ‚ČĘ Trim description) @
{ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"identity_mode_invalid", "identity mode must be ordinary or durable"‚ü©}‚ćü(¬¨ ((identityMode ‚Č° "ordinary") ‚ą® identityMode ‚Č° "durable")) @
{ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"event_id_unexpected", "ordinary actual must not carry an event-id"‚ü©}‚ćü((identityMode ‚Č° "ordinary") ‚ąß 0 < ‚Č† eventId) @
{ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"event_id_invalid", "event-id must be nonempty and must not contain unsafe control input"‚ü©}‚ćü((identityMode ‚Č° "durable") ‚ąß ((0 = ‚Č† Trim eventId) ‚ą® (UnsafeText eventId) ‚ą® eventId ‚ČĘ Trim eventId)) @
{ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"posting_count_invalid", "at least two --posting values are required"‚ü©}‚ćü(2 > ‚Č† postingArgs) @

postings ‚Üź empty
{ūĚēä text:
  equalMask ‚Üź '=' = text
  {ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"posting_shape_invalid", "each posting must contain exactly one ACCOUNT=SIGNED_INTEGER pair"‚ü©}‚ćü(1 ‚Č† +¬ī equalMask) @
  equalIndex ‚Üź ‚äĎ equalMask / ‚Üē ‚Č† text
  account ‚Üź equalIndex ‚ÜĎ text
  amountText ‚Üź (equalIndex + 1) ‚Üď text
  {ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"posting_shape_invalid", "posting account and amount must both be nonempty"‚ü©}‚ćü((0 = ‚Č† account) ‚ą® 0 = ‚Č† amountText) @
  {ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"posting_account_invalid", "posting account contains unsafe control input"‚ü©}‚ćü(UnsafeText account) @
  negative ‚Üź '-' = ‚äĎ (amountText ‚ąĺ "0")
  unsigned ‚Üź negative ‚Üď amountText
  parsedAmount ‚Üź decimal.Parse unsigned
  exactInteger ‚Üź (parsedAmount.state ‚Č° "ok") ‚ąß (0 = parsedAmount.scale) ‚ąß unsigned ‚Č° ‚ÄĘFmt parsedAmount.coefficient
  {ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"posting_amount_invalid", "posting amount must be a canonical nonzero exact integer"‚ü©}‚ćü(¬¨ exactInteger) @
  delta ‚Üź (1 - 2 √ó negative) √ó parsedAmount.coefficient
  {ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"posting_amount_zero", "posting amount must be nonzero"‚ü©}‚ćü(0 = delta) @
  canonical ‚Üź negative ‚ó∂ ‚ü®{‚ÄĘFmt parsedAmount.coefficient}, {"-" ‚ąĺ ‚ÄĘFmt parsedAmount.coefficient}‚ü© @
  {ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"posting_amount_invalid", "posting amount must be a canonical signed integer"‚ü©}‚ćü(amountText ‚ČĘ canonical) @
  postings ‚ąĺ‚Ü© ‚ü®{account_key‚áźaccount, amount_text‚áźamountText, delta‚áźdelta, commodity‚áź"JPY"}‚ü©
}¬® postingArgs
{ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"event_unbalanced", "signed posting amounts must sum exactly to zero"‚ü©}‚ćü(0 ‚Č† +¬ī {ūĚē©.delta}¬® postings) @

legacyKeys ‚Üź ‚ü®"tax","biz","invoice","note","due_on","receipt","txn_id","party","plan_id","cashflow","currency","recur","series"‚ü©
nativeKeys ‚Üź ‚ü®"tax","biz","invoice","note","due-on","receipt","txn-id","party","plan-id","cashflow","currency","recur","series"‚ü©
metadata ‚Üź empty
{ūĚēä text:
  equalMask ‚Üź '='=text
  {ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"metadata_shape_invalid", "each metadata item must contain exactly one key=value pair"‚ü©}‚ćü(1‚Č†+¬īequalMask) @
  equalIndex ‚Üź ‚äĎequalMask/‚Üē‚Č†text
  key ‚Üź equalIndex‚ÜĎtext ‚čĄ value ‚Üź (equalIndex+1)‚Üďtext
  keyIndex ‚Üź ‚äĎlegacyKeys‚äź‚ü®key‚ü©
  {ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"metadata_key_invalid", "metadata key is not supported by the native Journal profile"‚ü©}‚ćü(keyIndex=‚Č†legacyKeys) @
  {ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"metadata_value_invalid", "metadata value must be nonempty and structurally safe"‚ü©}‚ćü((0=‚Č†value)‚ą®(UnsafeText value)‚ą®(value‚ČĘTrim value)) @
  metadata ‚ąĺ‚Ü© ‚ü®{key‚áźkeyIndex‚äĎnativeKeys,value‚áźvalue}‚ü©
}¬®metadataArgs
metadataKeys ‚Üź {ūĚē©.key}¬®metadata
{ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"metadata_duplicate", "metadata keys must be unique"‚ü©}‚ćü((‚Č†metadataKeys)‚Č†‚Č†‚ć∑metadataKeys) @
{ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"ordinary_plan_link_invalid", "ordinary actual cannot carry plan-id; use a durable plan completion path"‚ü©}‚ćü((identityMode ‚Č° "ordinary") ‚ąß ‚ą®¬ī 0 ‚ąĺ "plan-id"‚äł‚Č°¬® metadataKeys) @

raw ‚Üź loader.ReadRaw target
existing ‚Üź parser.ParseWithProfile ‚ü®raw,"historical_external_plan"‚ü©
{ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"existing_journal_invalid", "existing complete Journal does not satisfy the supported profile"‚ü©}‚ćü(existing.state ‚ČĘ "ok") @
