resolved ‚Üź ak.Resolve loader.ReadLines (base ‚ąĺ "/accounts.tsv")
{ūĚēä posting:
  registryMask ‚Üź posting.account_key‚äł‚Č°¬® resolved.accounts
  {ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"posting_account_unresolved", "posting account must resolve exactly once in accounts.tsv"‚ü©}‚ćü(1 ‚Č† +¬ī registryMask) @
  idx ‚Üź ‚äĎ registryMask / ‚Üē ‚Č† registryMask
  {ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"posting_currency_invalid", "every resolved posting account must use JPY"‚ü©}‚ćü("JPY" ‚ČĘ idx ‚äĎ resolved.currencies) @
}¬® postings

postingLines ‚Üź {"    " ‚ąĺ ūĚē©.account_key ‚ąĺ "    " ‚ąĺ ūĚē©.amount_text ‚ąĺ " JPY"}¬® postings
metadataLines ‚Üź {"    ; "‚ąĺūĚē©.key‚ąĺ": "‚ąĺūĚē©.value}¬®metadata
headerLines ‚Üź (identityMode ‚Č° "durable") ‚ó∂ ‚ü®{‚ü®dateText ‚ąĺ " * " ‚ąĺ description‚ü©}, {‚ü®dateText ‚ąĺ " * " ‚ąĺ description, "    ; event-id: " ‚ąĺ eventId‚ü©}‚ü© @
blockLines ‚Üź headerLines ‚ąĺ metadataLines ‚ąĺ postingLines
block ‚Üź ‚äĎ blockLines
{ūĚēä line: block ‚ąĺ‚Ü© lf ‚ąĺ line}¬® 1 ‚Üď blockLines

rawCount ‚Üź ‚Č† raw
endsOne ‚Üź (0 < rawCount) ‚ąß lf = ¬Į1 ‚äĎ raw
endsTwo ‚Üź (1 < rawCount) ‚ąß (lf = ¬Į1 ‚äĎ raw) ‚ąß lf = ¬Į2 ‚äĎ raw
semanticSeparator ‚Üź endsTwo ‚ó∂ ‚ü®{endsOne ‚ó∂ ‚ü®{lf ‚ąĺ lf}, {lf}‚ü© @}, {""}‚ü© @
transportPrefixCount ‚Üź endsTwo ‚ó∂ ‚ü®{1}, {0}‚ü© @
proposedRaw ‚Üź raw ‚ąĺ semanticSeparator ‚ąĺ block ‚ąĺ lf
proposed ‚Üź parser.ParseWithProfile ‚ü®proposedRaw,"historical_external_plan"‚ü©
{ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"proposed_journal_invalid", "exact proposed complete Journal does not satisfy the supported profile"‚ü©}‚ćü(proposed.state ‚ČĘ "ok") @
{ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"candidate_count_invalid", "proposed Journal must contain exactly one transaction beyond the existing transaction count"‚ü©}‚ćü((candidateOrdinal + 1) ‚ČĘ ‚Č† proposed.transactions) @

