{ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"posting_ir_invalid", "checked Stage 2A Posting IR rejected the proposed complete Journal"‚ü©}‚ćü(checked.state ‚ČĘ "ok") @

candidate ‚Üź candidateOrdinal ‚äĎ proposed.transactions

priorTransactions ‚Üź candidateOrdinal ‚ÜĎ proposed.transactions
priorEndLine ‚Üź (0 < candidateOrdinal) ‚ó∂ ‚ü®0, {‚Ćą¬ī {ūĚē©.source_end_line}¬® priorTransactions}‚ü© @
{ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"candidate_boundary_invalid", "candidate start line must be greater than prior end line"‚ü©}‚ćü(candidate.source_start_line ‚Č§ priorEndLine) @

candidateAccounts ‚Üź {ūĚē©.account_key}¬® candidate.postings
candidateAmounts ‚Üź {ūĚē©.delta}¬® candidate.postings
candidateCommodities ‚Üź {ūĚē©.commodity}¬® candidate.postings
expectedAccounts ‚Üź {ūĚē©.account_key}¬® postings
expectedAmounts ‚Üź {ūĚē©.delta}¬® postings
commoditiesOk ‚Üź ‚ąß¬ī {ūĚē© ‚Č° "JPY"}¬® candidateCommodities
eventMetadataCount ‚Üź +¬ī {ūĚē©.key ‚Č° "event-id"}¬® candidate.metadata
identityOk ‚Üź (identityMode ‚Č° "durable") ‚ó∂ ‚ü®
  {(candidate.identity_kind ‚Č° "physical_fallback") ‚ąß 0 = eventMetadataCount},
  {(candidate.identity_kind ‚Č° "durable") ‚ąß (candidate.source_event_id ‚Č° eventId) ‚ąß 1 = eventMetadataCount}
‚ü© @
candidateOk ‚Üź (candidate.date ‚Č° dateText) ‚ąß (candidate.description ‚Č° description) ‚ąß identityOk ‚ąß (candidate.layer_name ‚Č° "actual") ‚ąß (candidate.status_marker = '*') ‚ąß ((‚Č† candidate.postings) = ‚Č† postings) ‚ąß (candidateAccounts ‚Č° expectedAccounts) ‚ąß (candidateAmounts ‚Č° expectedAmounts) ‚ąß commoditiesOk
{ūĚēä‚čĄFail ‚ü®"candidate_mismatch", "parsed candidate does not exactly match the rendered candidate"‚ü©}‚ćü(¬¨ candidateOk) @

identityToken ‚Üź (identityMode ‚Č° "durable") ‚ó∂ ‚ü®{"-"}, {eventId}‚ü© @
‚ÄĘOut "OK" ‚ąĺ tab ‚ąĺ "APPEND_BLOCK" ‚ąĺ tab ‚ąĺ (‚ÄĘFmt transportPrefixCount) ‚ąĺ tab ‚ąĺ identityMode ‚ąĺ tab ‚ąĺ identityToken ‚ąĺ tab ‚ąĺ (‚ÄĘFmt ‚Č† postings) ‚ąĺ tab ‚ąĺ (‚ÄĘFmt candidateOrdinal)
‚ÄĘOut block
